                            "text_bNwWVV": {
                              "type": "text",
                              "name": "t:names.text",
                              "settings": {
                                "text": "<p>Soft and supple from day one, suede is a versatile material which can easily add bold colour or unexpected texture to your outfit. It’s full of character and makes the perfect partner to our distinctive boots and shoes. Suede is unique because it’s made from the underside of the hide, making it soft and flexible. It also feels fuzzy to the touch — referred to as the “nap” — which can vary in length, resulting in a statement textured finish. ​The delicate nature of suede leather can make shoe care seem daunting — but we’ve put together our best tips and tricks for cleaning and maintaining it. Look no further than our <a href=\"https://www.drmartens.com/uk/en_gb/ultra-shoe-protector-150ml-black/p/AC770000\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">suede care guide</span></a>.</p>",
